Package bacnet.expressionAtlas.core

Class ComparisonAtlas

java.lang.Object
bacnet.expressionAtlas.core.ComparisonAtlas
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ComparisonAtlas extends Object implements Serializable
A ComparisonAtlas is related to a Comparison object and gives the list of genome elements over, under and not differentially expressed
Author:
UIBC

    ComparisonAtlas()
     
    ComparisonAtlas(ExpressionMatrix logFCMatrix, ArrayList<String> excludeColumns, String comparisonName, Filter filter)
    For a specific biological condition comparison update the list of genome elements in which the genome element is over-expressed, under-expressed or not differently expressed
    The update will be dependent of the value of the input filter = cutoff for LogFC and p-value

    • load

      public static ComparisonAtlas load(String fileName)
      Read compressed, serialized data with a FileInputStream. Uncompress that data with a GZIPInputStream. Deserialize the vector of lines with a ObjectInputStream. Replace current data with new data, and redraw everything.

    • save

      public void save(String fileName)
      Serialize the vector of lines with an ObjectOutputStream. Compress the serialized objects with a GZIPOutputStream. Write the compressed, serialized data to a file with a FileOutputStream. Don't forget to flush and close the stream.
